      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and entirely free from cosmetic or mechanical imperfections, it offers an uncompromising experience for the discerning enthusiast. Every detail reflects a rigorous standard of care, ensuring its status as a premier example of the marque.",
